title: Seattle's neo-soul, psych R&B band Day Soul Exquisite is now Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Day Soul Exquisite performing “Abattoir” live in the KEXP studio. Recorded January 23, 2024

Francesca Eluhu - Vocals, Guitar
